data.description: Fall in love with this charming 3-bedroom starter home!This light and bright gem boasts a recently remodeled kitchen, perfect for whipping up culinary delights. Enjoy the ease of meal prep with ample counter space and sparkling new appliances. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the kitchen to the living area, creating a perfect space for entertaining or family gatherings. Cozy up by the inviting fireplace on chilly nights, adding warmth and ambiance.Step outside to your fully fenced backyard, ideal for barbecues, playtime, or relaxing under the sun. Whether you have furry friends or little ones, the fenced-in space provides peace of mind and a safe haven for outdoor fun.This delightful home offers a comfortable blend of tile and carpet flooring, catering to both style and practicality. The indoor laundry room adds convenience, eliminating the need for trips to the laundromat. And for those DIY projects or extra storage, the partially converted garage provides valuable flexibility.Location, location, location! This charmer sits close to schools and shopping, making your daily errands a breeze. Enjoy the convenience of having everything you need within easy reach.Don't miss out on this move-in ready gem! This charming starter home is perfect for young families, first-time buyers, or anyone seeking a comfortable and convenient place to call their own.
